What it does

The script day-2.py creates an in-memory task list using Python list and dict, updates task status, and uses conditionals to check progress.
It also demonstrates mutability by showing how changes to one reference affect the original list.

Automation

Every time I push code to GitHub, GitHub Actions automatically runs the Python script and marks the build as success or failure.